    id_b: prepackaged ice cream

The icecream machine is broken and you need to decide how to replace it:
    Options:
    id_a: new machine
    id_b: prepackaged ice cream

    You can only stock one type of new product. Reason about which would be a better choice.

I'll choose the new machine (id_a). While prepackaged ice cream offers immediate convenience, a working machine allows customers to create their own custom treats, enhancing the shop's charm and offering a unique experience. Freshly made ice cream also has higher perceived value. The long-term investment in a machine will pay off through repeat customers and the ability to offer seasonal flavors, aligning with our goal of both profitability and customer satisfaction.
